				<h2>Politique de Confidentialité</h2>
				<div style="position: absolute; right: 20px; top: 10px;">
					<span class="txt16blancobold" style="cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline; padding-right: 30px;" onclick="javascript:window.print();">Imprimer</span> 
